 <sect1 xml:id="sec.adm.docupdates.5maint2">
  <title>February 2018 (Documentation Maintenance Update)</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>General Updates</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Inserted <xref linkend="Deepsea.restart"/> into
        <xref
       linkend="ceph.operating.services"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ds.mon"/>
        <link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1038731"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ogw.bucket_sharding.dyn"/>
        <link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1076001"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ogw.bucket_sharding"/>
        <link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1076000"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated the &rgw; SSL the &deepsea; way in
        <xref linkend="ceph.rgw.https"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1083756"/>
        and
        <link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1077809"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Changes in &deepsea; require a modified deployment of &ganesha; with
        &rgw;. See <xref linkend="ceph.nfsganesha.customrole.rgw_multiusers"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1058821"/>).
        <command>ceph osd pool create</command> fails if placement group limit
        per OSD is exceeded. See <xref linkend="ceph.pools.operate.add_pool"/>.
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1076509"/>)
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a reliability warning in <xref linkend="ceph.config.runtime"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=989349"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ogw.deploy"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1088895"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed <literal>lz4</literal> from the list of compression algorithms
        in <xref linkend="sec.ceph.pool.bluestore_compression.options"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1088450"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a tip on removing multiple OSDs in
        <xref linkend="salt.removing.osd"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1070791"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="tips.stopping_osd_without_rebalancing"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1051039"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added MDS cache size configurables in
        <xref linkend="ceph.cephfs.mds.config"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1062692"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ogw.keystone"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1077941"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a tip about synchronizing &igw; configuration in
        <xref
         linkend="ceph.iscsi.rbd.export"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1073327"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Changes in &deepsea; require a modified deployment of &ganesha; with
        &rgw;. See <xref linkend="ceph.nfsganesha.customrole.rgw_multiusers"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1058821"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
 <sect1 xml:id="sec.adm.docupdates.5maint1">
  <title>November 2017 (Documentation Maintenance Update)</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>General Updates</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Add section about adding a disk to OSD nodes. See
        <xref linkend="salt.node.add-disk"/>.
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1066005"/>)
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="storage.bd.replacing_disk"/> (Fate #321032).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ec.rbd"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1075158"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <command>salt-run remove.osd</command> requires OSD_ID digit without
        leading <literal>osd.</literal>. See
        <xref linkend="salt.removing.osd"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <command>ceph tell</command> requires OSD_ID digit and leading
        <literal>osd.</literal>. See
        <xref linkend="storage.bp.performance.slowosd"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="trouble.jobcache"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1069255"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="sec.ceph.rgw.limits"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1067613"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Fixed rbd-mirror starting and stopping commands in
        <xref linkend="rbd.mirror.daemon"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1068061"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
 </sect1>
 <sect1 xml:id="sec.adm.docupdates.5">
  <title>October, 2017 (Release of &productname; 5)</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>General Updates</term>
    <listitem>
     <para/>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed Calamari in favor of &oa;.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="oa.webui.nfs"/> (Fate #321620).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ceph.rbd.rbdmap"/>
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ceph.rbd"/> (Fate #321061).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="oa.webui.rgw_users"/> (Fate #320318).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ceph.rgw.ldap"/> (Fate #321631).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ceph.cephfs.activeactive"/> (Fate #322976).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="oa.webui.iscsi"/> (Fate #321370).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added &igw; and &rgw; configuration for &oa;, see
        <xref linkend="oa.rgw"/> and <xref linkend="oa.igw"/> (Fate #320318 and
        #321370).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated <xref linkend="cha.ceph.nfsganesha"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1036495"/>,
        <link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1031444"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        RBD images can now be stored in EC pools, see
        <xref linkend="ceph.rbd.cmds.create-ec"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1040752"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added section about backing up &deepsea; configuration, see
        <xref linkend="cha.deployment_backup"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1046497"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        &rgw; failover and disaster recovery, see
        <xref linkend="ceph.rgw.fed.failover"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1036084"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        &bluestore; enables data compression for pools, see
        <xref linkend="sec.ceph.pool.compression"/> (FATE#318582).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        CIFS export of &cephfs; is possible, see <xref linkend="cha.ses.cifs"/>
        (FATE#321622).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added procedure for cluster reboot, see
        <xref linkend="sec.salt.cluster.reboot"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1047638"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        &deepsea; stage 0 can update without rebooting, see
        <xref linkend="deepsea.rolling_updates"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        <command>ceph fs</command> replaced, see
        <xref linkend="cephfs.activeactive.decrease"/> and
        <xref linkend="cephfs.activeactive.increase"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1047638"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added section <xref linkend="storage.bp.network_test"/> (FATE#321031).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Bugfixes</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist mark="bullet" spacing="normal">
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated command output to reflect storage classes in
        <xref linkend="op.mixed_ssd_hdd"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1061299"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        The swift client package is now part of the 'Public Cloud' module in
        <xref linkend="accessing.ragos.gateway"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1057591"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ceph.config.runtime"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1061435"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Changed a command into a configuration option in
        <xref linkend="op.mixed_ssd_hdd"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1059561"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated <command>ceph osd pool set</command> command to match Luminous
        syntax in <xref linkend="op.mixed_ssd_hdd"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1059593"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Civetweb binds to multiple ports in
        <xref linkend="rgw.civetweb.multiport"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1055181"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Included 3 &ogw; options affecting performance in
        <xref linkend="sec.ceph.rgw.configuration"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1052983"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Imported <xref linkend="ds.custom.cephconf"/> and added the need for
        Stage 3
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1057273"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added libvirt keyring creation in
        <xref linkend="ceph.libvirt.cfg_ceph"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1055610"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added <xref linkend="ex.ds.rmnode"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1054516"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated <xref linkend="monitor.watch"/>
        (<link xlink:href="https://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1053638"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Made Salt REST API variables optional in
        <xref linkend="ceph.oa.installation"/>
